data.description: The search is finally over! Gorgeous 3-bedroom residence located in Stonehaven waiting for you! Discover a bright & spacious open layout showcasing neutral tile floor, fresh soothing palette, & stylish light fixtures. The stunning chef's kitchen is a cook's delight offering cabinets w/crown moulding, granite counters, wall oven, SS appliances, a pantry, & a convenient center island including a breakfast bar. The versatile loft is the perfect spot for an entertainment area or playroom! End your busy day in the main retreat comprised of soft carpet, an ensuite w/dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. Enjoy hosting fun gatherings in the oversized backyard w/a covered patio, Gazebo & hot tub . Don't miss this value!!
